02219             interface_ip.pure_cam            = false;
02220             interface_ip.pure_ram            = false;
02221             interface_ip.line_sz             = data;
02222             interface_ip.cache_sz            = data*XML->sys.core[ithCore].phy_Regs_IRF_size;
02223             interface_ip.assoc               = 0;
02224             interface_ip.nbanks              = 1;
02225             interface_ip.out_w               = out_w*8;
02226             interface_ip.specific_tag        = 1;
02227             interface_ip.tag_w               = tag;
02228             interface_ip.access_mode         = 2;
02229             interface_ip.throughput          = 1.0/clockRate;
02230             interface_ip.latency             = 1.0/clockRate;
02231             interface_ip.obj_func_dyn_energy = 0;
02232             interface_ip.obj_func_dyn_power  = 0;
02233             interface_ip.obj_func_leak_power = 0;
02234             interface_ip.obj_func_cycle_t    = 1;
02235             interface_ip.num_rw_ports    = 1;//for GCs
02236             interface_ip.num_rd_ports    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].decode_width;//0;TODO
02237             interface_ip.num_wr_ports    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].decode_width;
02238             interface_ip.num_se_rd_ports = 0;
02239             interface_ip.num_search_ports= 2*XML->sys.core[ithCore].decode_width;
02240             iFRAT = new ArrayST(&interface_ip, "Int FrontRAT", Core_device, coredynp.opt_local, coredynp.core_ty);
02241             iFRAT->area.set_area(iFRAT->area.get_area()+ iFRAT->local_result.area*XML->sys.core[ithCore].number_hardware_threads);
02242             area.set_area(area.get_area()+ iFRAT->area.get_area());
02243 
02244             //FRAT
02245             tag                              = coredynp.arch_freg_width;
02246             data                             = int(ceil (coredynp.arch_freg_width+1*coredynp.globalCheckpoint/8.0));//the address of CAM needed to be sent out
02247             out_w                            = int(ceil (coredynp.arch_freg_width/8.0));
02248             interface_ip.is_cache            = true;
02249             interface_ip.pure_cam            = false;
02250             interface_ip.pure_ram            = false;
02251             interface_ip.line_sz             = data;
02252             interface_ip.cache_sz            = data*XML->sys.core[ithCore].phy_Regs_FRF_size;
02253             interface_ip.assoc               = 0;
02254             interface_ip.nbanks              = 1;
02255             interface_ip.out_w               = out_w*8;
02256             interface_ip.specific_tag        = 1;
02257             interface_ip.tag_w               = tag;
02258             interface_ip.access_mode         = 2;
02259             interface_ip.throughput          = 1.0/clockRate;
02260             interface_ip.latency             = 1.0/clockRate;
02261             interface_ip.obj_func_dyn_energy = 0;
02262             interface_ip.obj_func_dyn_power  = 0;
02263             interface_ip.obj_func_leak_power = 0;
02264             interface_ip.obj_func_cycle_t    = 1;
02265             interface_ip.num_rw_ports    = 1;//for GCs
02266             interface_ip.num_rd_ports    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].decode_width;//0;TODO;
02267             interface_ip.num_wr_ports    = coredynp.fp_decodeW;
02268             interface_ip.num_se_rd_ports = 0;
02269             interface_ip.num_search_ports= 2*coredynp.fp_decodeW;
02270             fFRAT = new ArrayST(&interface_ip, "Int FrontRAT", Core_device, coredynp.opt_local, coredynp.core_ty);
02271             fFRAT->area.set_area(fFRAT->area.get_area()+ fFRAT->local_result.area*XML->sys.core[ithCore].number_hardware_threads);
02272             area.set_area(area.get_area()+ fFRAT->area.get_area());
02273 
02274         }
02275         //No RRAT for RS based OOO
02276         //Freelist of renaming unit of RS based OOO is unifed for both int and fp renaming unit since the ROB is unified
02277         data                             = int(ceil(coredynp.phy_ireg_width/8.0));
02278         interface_ip.is_cache            = false;
02279         interface_ip.pure_cam            = false;
02280         interface_ip.pure_ram            = true;
02281         interface_ip.line_sz             = data;
02282         interface_ip.cache_sz            = data*coredynp.num_ifreelist_entries;
02283         interface_ip.assoc               = 1;
02284         interface_ip.nbanks              = 1;
02285         interface_ip.out_w               = interface_ip.line_sz*8;
02286         interface_ip.access_mode         = 1;
02287         interface_ip.throughput          = 1.0/clockRate;
02288         interface_ip.latency             = 1.0/clockRate;
02289         interface_ip.obj_func_dyn_energy = 0;
02290         interface_ip.obj_func_dyn_power  = 0;
02291         interface_ip.obj_func_leak_power = 0;
02292         interface_ip.obj_func_cycle_t    = 1;
02293         interface_ip.num_rw_ports    = 1;//TODO
02294         interface_ip.num_rd_ports    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].decode_width;
02295         interface_ip.num_wr_ports    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].decode_width -1 + XML->sys.core[ithCore].commit_width;
02296         interface_ip.num_se_rd_ports = 0;
02297         ifreeL = new ArrayST(&interface_ip, "Unified Free List", Core_device, coredynp.opt_local, coredynp.core_ty);
02298         ifreeL->area.set_area(ifreeL->area.get_area()+ ifreeL->local_result.area*XML->sys.core[ithCore].number_hardware_threads);
02299         area.set_area(area.get_area()+ ifreeL->area.get_area());
02300 
02301         idcl  = new dep_resource_conflict_check(&interface_ip,coredynp,coredynp.phy_ireg_width);//TODO:Separate 2 sections See TR
02302         fdcl  = new dep_resource_conflict_check(&interface_ip,coredynp,coredynp.phy_freg_width);
02303     }
02304 
02305 }
02306     if (coredynp.core_ty==Inorder&& coredynp.issueW>1)
02307     {
02308       /* Dependency check logic will only present when decode(issue) width>1.
02309       *  Multiple issue in order processor can do without renaming, but dcl is a must.
02310       */
02311     idcl  = new dep_resource_conflict_check(&interface_ip,coredynp,coredynp.phy_ireg_width);//TODO:Separate 2 sections See TR
02312     fdcl  = new dep_resource_conflict_check(&interface_ip,coredynp,coredynp.phy_freg_width);
02313     }
02314 }

02325  corepipe (0),
02326  undiffCore (0),
02327  l2cache (0)
02328 {
02332   //XML->sys.core[ithCore].simd_width=8;// (8)

02338   * initialize, compute and optimize individual components.
02339   */

02347

02349 //  interface_ip.wire_is_mat_type = 2;

02361

02389       area.set_area(area.get_area() + ifu->area.get_area());

02392   {

02394       area.set_area(area.get_area() + lsu->area.get_area());
02395   }
02396   if (exu->exist)
02397   {
02398       exu->area.set_area(exu->area.get_area() + pipeline_area_per_unit);
02399       area.set_area(area.get_area()+exu->area.get_area());
02400   }
02401   if (mmu->exist)
02402   {
02403       mmu->area.set_area(mmu->area.get_area() + pipeline_area_per_unit);
02404       area.set_area(area.get_area()+mmu->area.get_area());
02405   }
02406 
02407   if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
02408   {
02409       if (rnu->exist)
02410       {
02411

02413       }
02414   }
02415

02419   }
02420

02434 
02435 
02436 void BranchPredictor::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
02437 {
02438     if (!exist) return;
02439     double r_access;
02440     double w_access;
02441     if (is_tdp)
02442     {
02443         r_access = coredynp.predictionW*coredynp.BR_duty_cycle;
02444         w_access = 0*coredynp.BR_duty_cycle;
02445         globalBPT->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02446         globalBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02447         globalBPT->tdp_stats = globalBPT->stats_t;
02448 
02449         L1_localBPT->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02450         L1_localBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02451         L1_localBPT->tdp_stats = L1_localBPT->stats_t;
02452 
02453         L2_localBPT->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02454         L2_localBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02455         L2_localBPT->tdp_stats = L2_localBPT->stats_t;
02456 
02457         chooser->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02458         chooser->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02459         chooser->tdp_stats = chooser->stats_t;
02460 
02461         RAS->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02462         RAS->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02463         RAS->tdp_stats = RAS->stats_t;
02464     }
02465     else
02466     {
02467         //The resolution of BPT accesses is coarse, but this is
02468         //because most simulators cannot track finer grained details
02469         r_access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].branch_instructions;
02470         w_access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].branch_mispredictions + 0.1*XML->sys.core[ithCore].branch_instructions;//10% of BR will flip internal bits//0
02471         globalBPT->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02472         globalBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02473         globalBPT->rtp_stats = globalBPT->stats_t;
02474 
02475         L1_localBPT->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02476         L1_localBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02477         L1_localBPT->rtp_stats = L1_localBPT->stats_t;
02478 
02479         L2_localBPT->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02480         L2_localBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02481         L2_localBPT->rtp_stats = L2_localBPT->stats_t;
02482 
02483         chooser->stats_t.readAc.access  = r_access;
02484         chooser->stats_t.writeAc.access = w_access;
02485         chooser->rtp_stats = chooser->stats_t;
02486 
02487         RAS->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls;
02488         RAS->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls;
02489         RAS->rtp_stats = RAS->stats_t;
02490    }
02491 
02492     globalBPT->power_t.reset();
02493     L1_localBPT->power_t.reset();
02494     L2_localBPT->power_t.reset();
02495     chooser->power_t.reset();
02496     RAS->power_t.reset();
02497 
02498     globalBPT->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  globalBPT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*globalBPT->stats_t.readAc.access +
02499                 globalBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access*globalBPT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02500     L1_localBPT->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  L1_localBPT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*L1_localBPT->stats_t.readAc.access +
02501                 L1_localBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access*L1_localBPT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02502 
02503     L2_localBPT->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  L2_localBPT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*L2_localBPT->stats_t.readAc.access +
02504                 L2_localBPT->stats_t.writeAc.access*L2_localBPT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02505 
02506     chooser->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  chooser->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*chooser->stats_t.readAc.access +
02507                 chooser->stats_t.writeAc.access*chooser->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02508     RAS->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  RAS->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*RAS->stats_t.readAc.access +
02509                 RAS->stats_t.writeAc.access*RAS->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02510 
02511     if (is_tdp)
02512     {
02513         globalBPT->power = globalBPT->power_t + globalBPT->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02514         L1_localBPT->power = L1_localBPT->power_t + L1_localBPT->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02515         L2_localBPT->power = L2_localBPT->power_t + L2_localBPT->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02516         chooser->power = chooser->power_t + chooser->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02517         RAS->power = RAS->power_t + RAS->local_result.power*coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
02518 
02519         power = power + globalBPT->power + L1_localBPT->power + chooser->power + RAS->power;
02520     }
02521     else
02522     {
02523         globalBPT->rt_power = globalBPT->power_t + globalBPT->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02524         L1_localBPT->rt_power = L1_localBPT->power_t + L1_localBPT->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02525         L2_localBPT->rt_power = L2_localBPT->power_t + L2_localBPT->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02526         chooser->rt_power = chooser->power_t + chooser->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02527         RAS->rt_power = RAS->power_t + RAS->local_result.power*coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
02528         rt_power = rt_power + globalBPT->rt_power + L1_localBPT->rt_power + chooser->rt_power + RAS->rt_power;
02529     }
02530 }

02561             << (long_channel? L2_localBPT->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:L2_localBPT->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
02562         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << L2_localBPT->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
02563         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << L2_localBPT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;

02565

02568         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << chooser->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02569         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
02570             << (long_channel? chooser->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:chooser->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
02571         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << chooser->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;

02600 
02601 void InstFetchU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
02602 {
02603   executionTime=XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6);//Syed
02604   //cout <<"IFU: execution time: "<<XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6)<<endl;
02605   //cout <<"IFU: total cycles"<<XML->sys.total_cycles<<endl;
02606     if (!exist) return;
02607     if (is_tdp)
02608     {
02609         //init stats for Peak
02610         icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.access  = icache.caches->l_ip.num_rw_ports*coredynp.IFU_duty_cycle;
02611         icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss    = 0;
02612         icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit     = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.access - icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02613         icache.caches->tdp_stats = icache.caches->stats_t;
02614 
02615         icache.missb->stats_t.readAc.access  = icache.missb->stats_t.readAc.hit=  icache.missb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02616         icache.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access = icache.missb->stats_t.writeAc.hit= icache.missb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02617         icache.missb->tdp_stats = icache.missb->stats_t;
02618 
02619         icache.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access  = icache.ifb->stats_t.readAc.hit=  icache.ifb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02620         icache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access = icache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.hit= icache.ifb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02621         icache.ifb->tdp_stats = icache.ifb->stats_t;
02622 
02623         icache.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access  = icache.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.hit= icache.prefetchb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02624         icache.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access = icache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.hit= icache.ifb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02625         icache.prefetchb->tdp_stats = icache.prefetchb->stats_t;
02626 
02627         IB->stats_t.readAc.access = IB->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].peak_issue_width;
02628         IB->tdp_stats = IB->stats_t;
02629 
02630         if (coredynp.predictionW>0)
02631         {
02632             BTB->stats_t.readAc.access  = coredynp.predictionW;//XML->sys.core[ithCore].BTB.read_accesses;
02633             BTB->stats_t.writeAc.access = 0;//XML->sys.core[ithCore].BTB.write_accesses;
02634         }
02635 
02636         ID_inst->stats_t.readAc.access     = coredynp.decodeW;
02637         ID_operand->stats_t.readAc.access  = coredynp.decodeW;
02638         ID_misc->stats_t.readAc.access     = coredynp.decodeW;
02639         ID_inst->tdp_stats = ID_inst->stats_t;
02640         ID_operand->tdp_stats = ID_operand->stats_t;
02641         ID_misc->tdp_stats = ID_misc->stats_t;
02642 
02643 
02644    
02645      } /* if (is_tdp) */
02646     else
02647     {
02648       rt_power.reset();
02649       icache.rt_power.reset(); //Jingwen
02650         //init stats for Runtime Dynamic (RTP)
02651         //cout<< "****>>>>Icache stats:"<<endl;
02652         //cout<<"Read accesses: "<< XML->sys.core[ithCore].icache.read_accesses << " Read misses: "<<XML->sys.core[ithCore].icache.read_misses<<endl;
02653         icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].icache.read_accesses;
02654         icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].icache.read_misses;
02655         //cout<<endl<<"inside mcpat read access= "<<XML->sys.core[ithCore].icache.read_accesses;
02656         //cout<<endl<<"inside mcpat read miss= "<<XML->sys.core[ithCore].icache.read_misses;
02657 
02658         icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit     = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.access - icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02659         icache.caches->rtp_stats = icache.caches->stats_t;
02660         //cout<<endl<<"inside mcpat read hit= "<<icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit<<endl;
02661         icache.missb->stats_t.readAc.access  = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02662         icache.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02663         icache.missb->rtp_stats = icache.missb->stats_t;
02664 
02665         icache.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access  = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02666         icache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02667         icache.ifb->rtp_stats = icache.ifb->stats_t;
02668 
02669         icache.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access  = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02670         icache.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access = icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
02671         icache.prefetchb->rtp_stats = icache.prefetchb->stats_t;
02672 
02673         IB->stats_t.readAc.access = IB->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].total_instructions;
02674         IB->rtp_stats = IB->stats_t;
02675         //cout<<"IB: total instructions: "<<IB->stats_t.readAc.access <<endl;
02676         if (coredynp.predictionW>0)
02677         {
02678             BTB->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].BTB.read_accesses;//XML->sys.core[ithCore].branch_instructions;
02679             BTB->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].BTB.write_accesses;//XML->sys.core[ithCore].branch_mispredictions;
02680             BTB->rtp_stats = BTB->stats_t;
02681         }
02682         //cout<<"ID: total instructions: "<< XML->sys.core[ithCore].total_instructions<<endl;
02683         ID_inst->stats_t.readAc.access     = XML->sys.core[ithCore].total_instructions;
02684         ID_operand->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].total_instructions;
02685         ID_misc->stats_t.readAc.access     = XML->sys.core[ithCore].total_instructions;
02686         ID_inst->rtp_stats = ID_inst->stats_t;
02687         ID_operand->rtp_stats = ID_operand->stats_t;
02688         ID_misc->rtp_stats = ID_misc->stats_t;
02689 
02690     }
02691 
02692     icache.power_t.reset();
02693     IB->power_t.reset();
02694 //  ID_inst->power_t.reset();
02695 //  ID_operand->power_t.reset();
02696 //  ID_misc->power_t.reset();
02697     if (coredynp.predictionW>0)
02698     {
02699         BTB->power_t.reset();
02700     }
02701 
02702     icache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   += (icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit*icache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
02703             //icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss*icache.caches->local_result.tag_array2->power.readOp.dynamic+
02704             icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss*icache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+ //assume tag data accessed in parallel
02705             icache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss*icache.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic); //read miss in Icache cause a write to Icache
02706     icache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  icache.missb->stats_t.readAc.access*icache.missb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
02707             icache.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access*icache.missb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//each access to missb involves a CAM and a write
02708     icache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  icache.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access*icache.ifb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
02709             icache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access*icache.ifb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02710     icache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  icache.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access*icache.prefetchb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
02711             icache.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access*icache.prefetchb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02712    //cout<<"Icache power: "<<icache.power_t.readOp.dynamic  <<endl;
02713     IB->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  IB->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*IB->stats_t.readAc.access +
02714             IB->stats_t.writeAc.access*IB->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02715   //cout << "IB power: "<<IB->power_t.readOp.dynamic<<endl;
02716     if (coredynp.predictionW>0)
02717     {
02718         BTB->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  BTB->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*BTB->stats_t.readAc.access +
02719         BTB->stats_t.writeAc.access*BTB->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
02720 
02721         BPT->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
02722     }
02723 
02724     if (is_tdp)
02725     {
02726 //      icache.power = icache.power_t +
02727 //              (icache.caches->local_result.power)*pppm_lkg +
02728 //              (icache.missb->local_result.power +
02729 //              icache.ifb->local_result.power +
02730 //              icache.prefetchb->local_result.power)*pppm_Isub;
02731         icache.power = icache.power_t +
02732                 (icache.caches->local_result.power +
02733                 icache.missb->local_result.power +
02734                 icache.ifb->local_result.power +
02735                 icache.prefetchb->local_result.power)*pppm_lkg;
02736 
02737         IB->power = IB->power_t + IB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02738         power     = power + icache.power + IB->power;
02739         if (coredynp.predictionW>0)
02740         {
02741             BTB->power = BTB->power_t + BTB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02742             power     = power  + BTB->power + BPT->power;
02743         }
02744 
02745         ID_inst->power_t.readOp.dynamic    = ID_inst->power.readOp.dynamic;
02746         ID_operand->power_t.readOp.dynamic = ID_operand->power.readOp.dynamic;
02747         ID_misc->power_t.readOp.dynamic    = ID_misc->power.readOp.dynamic;
02748 
02749         ID_inst->power.readOp.dynamic    *= ID_inst->tdp_stats.readAc.access;
02750         ID_operand->power.readOp.dynamic *= ID_operand->tdp_stats.readAc.access;
02751         ID_misc->power.readOp.dynamic    *= ID_misc->tdp_stats.readAc.access;
02752 
02753         power = power + (ID_inst->power +
02754                             ID_operand->power +
02755                             ID_misc->power);
02756      } /* if (is_tdp) */ 
02757     else
02758     {
02759 //      icache.rt_power = icache.power_t +
02760 //              (icache.caches->local_result.power)*pppm_lkg +
02761 //              (icache.missb->local_result.power +
02762 //              icache.ifb->local_result.power +
02763 //              icache.prefetchb->local_result.power)*pppm_Isub;
02764 
02765         icache.rt_power = icache.power_t +
02766                 (icache.caches->local_result.power +
02767                 icache.missb->local_result.power +
02768                 icache.ifb->local_result.power +
02769                 icache.prefetchb->local_result.power)*pppm_lkg;
02770 
02771         //IB->rt_power = IB->power_t + IB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02772         IB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic = IB->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic * IB->rtp_stats.readAc.access;
02773         IB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic += IB->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic * IB->rtp_stats.writeAc.access;
02774         rt_power     = rt_power + icache.rt_power + IB->rt_power;
02775         if (coredynp.predictionW>0)
02776         {
02777             BTB->rt_power = BTB->power_t + BTB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
02778             rt_power     = rt_power + BTB->rt_power + BPT->rt_power;
02779         }
02780 
02781         ID_inst->rt_power.readOp.dynamic    = ID_inst->power_t.readOp.dynamic*ID_inst->rtp_stats.readAc.access;
02782         ID_operand->rt_power.readOp.dynamic = ID_operand->power_t.readOp.dynamic * ID_operand->rtp_stats.readAc.access;
02783         ID_misc->rt_power.readOp.dynamic    = ID_misc->power_t.readOp.dynamic * ID_misc->rtp_stats.readAc.access;
02784 
02785         rt_power = rt_power + (ID_inst->rt_power +
02786                             ID_operand->rt_power +
02787                             ID_misc->rt_power);
02788         //cout<<"ID inst: "<<ID_inst->rt_power.readOp.dynamic << " ID operand: "<<ID_operand->rt_power.readOp.dynamic<<" ID misc: "<<ID_misc->rt_power.readOp.dynamic<<endl;
02789     }
02790 }
02791 
02792 void InstFetchU::displayEnergy(uint32_t indent,int plevel,bool is_tdp)
02793 {
02794     if (!exist) return;
02795     string indent_str(indent, ' ');
02796     string indent_str_next(indent+2, ' ');
02797     bool long_channel = XML->sys.longer_channel_device;
02798 
02799 
02800     if (is_tdp)
02801     {
02802 
02803         cout << indent_str<< "Instruction Cache:" << endl;
02804         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << icache.area.get_area()*1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
02805         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << icache.power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
02806         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
02807             << (long_channel? icache.power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:icache.power.readOp.leakage) <<" W" << endl;
02808         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << icache.power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
02809         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << icache.rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
02810         cout <<endl;
02811         if (coredynp.predictionW>0)
02812         {
02813             cout << indent_str<< "Branch Target Buffer:" << endl;
02814             cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << BTB->area.get_area() *1e-6 << " mm^2" << endl;
02815             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << BTB->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02816             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
02817                 << (long_channel? BTB->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:BTB->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
02818             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << BTB->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
02819             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << BTB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
02820             cout <<endl;
02821             if (BPT->exist)
02822             {
02823                 cout << indent_str<< "Branch Predictor:" << endl;
02824                 cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << BPT->area.get_area()  *1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
02825                 cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << BPT->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02826                 cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
02827                     << (long_channel? BPT->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:BPT->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
02828                 cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << BPT->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
02829                 cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << BPT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
02830                 cout <<endl;
02831                 if (plevel>3)
02832                 {
02833                     BPT->displayEnergy(indent+4, plevel, is_tdp);
02834                 }
02835             }
02836         }
02837         cout << indent_str<< "Instruction Buffer:" << endl;
02838         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << IB->area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
02839         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << IB->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02840         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
02841         << (long_channel? IB->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:IB->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
02842         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << IB->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
02843         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << IB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
02844         cout <<endl;
02845         cout << indent_str<< "Instruction Decoder:" << endl;
02846         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << (ID_inst->area.get_area() +
02847                 ID_operand->area.get_area() +
02848                 ID_misc->area.get_area())*coredynp.decodeW*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
02849         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << (ID_inst->power.readOp.dynamic +
02850                 ID_operand->power.readOp.dynamic +
02851                 ID_misc->power.readOp.dynamic)*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02852         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
02853         << (long_channel? (ID_inst->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage +
02854                 ID_operand->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage +
02855                 ID_misc->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage):
02856                     (ID_inst->power.readOp.leakage +
02857                             ID_operand->power.readOp.leakage +
02858                             ID_misc->power.readOp.leakage))  << " W" << endl;
02859         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << (ID_inst->power.readOp.gate_leakage +
02860                 ID_operand->power.readOp.gate_leakage +
02861                 ID_misc->power.readOp.gate_leakage)  << " W" << endl;
02862         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << (ID_inst->rt_power.readOp.dynamic +
02863                 ID_operand->rt_power.readOp.dynamic +
02864                 ID_misc->rt_power.readOp.dynamic)/executionTime << " W" << endl;
02865         cout <<endl;
02866     }
02867     else
02868     {
02869 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Cache    Peak Dynamic = " << icache.rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
02870 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Cache    Subthreshold Leakage = " << icache.rt_power.readOp.leakage <<" W" << endl;
02871 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Cache    Gate Leakage = " << icache.rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
02872 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Buffer   Peak Dynamic = " << IB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02873 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Buffer   Subthreshold Leakage = " << IB->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
02874 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Buffer   Gate Leakage = " << IB->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
02875 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Branch Target Buffer   Peak Dynamic = " << BTB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02876 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Branch Target Buffer   Subthreshold Leakage = " << BTB->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
02877 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Branch Target Buffer   Gate Leakage = " << BTB->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
02878 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Branch Predictor   Peak Dynamic = " << BPT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
02879 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Branch Predictor   Subthreshold Leakage = " << BPT->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
02880 //      cout << indent_str_next << "Branch Predictor   Gate Leakage = " << BPT->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
02881     }
02882 
02883 }
02884 
02885 void RENAMINGU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
02886 {
02887     if (!exist) return;
02888     double pppm_t[4]    = {1,1,1,1};
02889     if (is_tdp)
02890     {//init stats for Peak
02891         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO){
02892             if (coredynp.scheu_ty==PhysicalRegFile)
02893             {
02894                 if (coredynp.rm_ty ==RAMbased)
02895                 {
02896                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = iFRAT->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02897                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = iFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02898                     iFRAT->tdp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
02899 
02900                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = fFRAT->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02901                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = fFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02902                     fFRAT->tdp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
02903 
02904                 }
02905                 else if ((coredynp.rm_ty ==CAMbased))
02906                 {
02907                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = iFRAT->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02908                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = iFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02909                     iFRAT->tdp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
02910 
02911                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = fFRAT->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02912                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = fFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02913                     fFRAT->tdp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
02914                 }
02915 
02916                 iRRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = iRRAT->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02917                 iRRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = iRRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02918                 iRRAT->tdp_stats = iRRAT->stats_t;
02919 
02920                 fRRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = fRRAT->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02921                 fRRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = fRRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02922                 fRRAT->tdp_stats = fRRAT->stats_t;
02923 
02924                 ifreeL->stats_t.readAc.access   = coredynp.decodeW;//ifreeL->l_ip.num_rd_ports;;
02925                 ifreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access  = coredynp.decodeW;//ifreeL->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02926                 ifreeL->tdp_stats = ifreeL->stats_t;
02927 
02928                 ffreeL->stats_t.readAc.access   = coredynp.decodeW;//ffreeL->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02929                 ffreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access  = coredynp.decodeW;//ffreeL->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02930                 ffreeL->tdp_stats = ffreeL->stats_t;
02931             }
02932             else if (coredynp.scheu_ty==ReservationStation){
02933                 if (coredynp.rm_ty ==RAMbased)
02934                 {
02935                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access    = iFRAT->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02936                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access   = iFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02937                     iFRAT->stats_t.searchAc.access  = iFRAT->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02938                     iFRAT->tdp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
02939 
02940                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access    = fFRAT->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02941                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access   = fFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02942                     fFRAT->stats_t.searchAc.access  = fFRAT->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02943                     fFRAT->tdp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
02944 
02945                 }
02946                 else if ((coredynp.rm_ty ==CAMbased))
02947                 {
02948                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = iFRAT->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02949                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = iFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02950                     iFRAT->tdp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
02951 
02952                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = fFRAT->l_ip.num_search_ports;
02953                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = fFRAT->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02954                     fFRAT->tdp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
02955                 }
02956                 //Unified free list for both int and fp
02957                 ifreeL->stats_t.readAc.access   = coredynp.decodeW;//ifreeL->l_ip.num_rd_ports;
02958                 ifreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access  = coredynp.decodeW;//ifreeL->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
02959                 ifreeL->tdp_stats = ifreeL->stats_t;
02960             }
02961             idcl->stats_t.readAc.access = coredynp.decodeW;
02962             fdcl->stats_t.readAc.access = coredynp.decodeW;
02963             idcl->tdp_stats = idcl->stats_t;
02964             fdcl->tdp_stats = fdcl->stats_t;
02965         }
02966         else
02967         {
02968             if (coredynp.issueW>1)
02969             {
02970                 idcl->stats_t.readAc.access = coredynp.decodeW;
02971                 fdcl->stats_t.readAc.access = coredynp.decodeW;
02972                 idcl->tdp_stats = idcl->stats_t;
02973                 fdcl->tdp_stats = fdcl->stats_t;
02974             }
02975         }
02976 
02977     }
02978     else
02979     {//init stats for Runtime Dynamic (RTP)
02980         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO){
02981             if (coredynp.scheu_ty==PhysicalRegFile)
02982             {
02983                 if (coredynp.rm_ty ==RAMbased)
02984                 {
02985                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_reads;
02986                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes;
02987                     iFRAT->rtp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
02988 
02989                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_reads;
02990                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;
02991                     fFRAT->rtp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
02992                 }
02993                 else if ((coredynp.rm_ty ==CAMbased))
02994                 {
02995                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_reads;
02996                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes;
02997                     iFRAT->rtp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
02998 
02999                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_reads;
03000                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;
03001                     fFRAT->rtp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
03002                 }
03003 
03004                 iRRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes;//Hack, should be (context switch + branch mispredictions)*16
03005                 iRRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes;
03006                 iRRAT->rtp_stats = iRRAT->stats_t;
03007 
03008                 fRRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;//Hack, should be (context switch + branch mispredictions)*16
03009                 fRRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;
03010                 fRRAT->rtp_stats = fRRAT->stats_t;
03011 
03012                 ifreeL->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_reads;
03013                 ifreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 2*XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes;
03014                 ifreeL->rtp_stats = ifreeL->stats_t;
03015 
03016                 ffreeL->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_reads;
03017                 ffreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 2*XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;
03018                 ffreeL->rtp_stats = ffreeL->stats_t;
03019             }
03020             else if (coredynp.scheu_ty==ReservationStation){
03021                 if (coredynp.rm_ty ==RAMbased)
03022                 {
03023                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_reads;
03024                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes;
03025                     iFRAT->stats_t.searchAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].committed_int_instructions;//hack: not all committed instructions use regs.
03026                     iFRAT->rtp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
03027 
03028                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_reads;
03029                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;
03030                     fFRAT->stats_t.searchAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].committed_fp_instructions;
03031                     fFRAT->rtp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
03032                 }
03033                 else if ((coredynp.rm_ty ==CAMbased))
03034                 {
03035                     iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_reads;
03036                     iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes;
03037                     iFRAT->rtp_stats = iFRAT->stats_t;
03038 
03039                     fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_reads;
03040                     fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;
03041                     fFRAT->rtp_stats = fFRAT->stats_t;
03042                 }
03043                 //Unified free list for both int and fp since the ROB act as physcial registers
03044                 ifreeL->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_reads +
03045                     XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_reads;
03046                 ifreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 2*(XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_writes +
03047                     XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes);//HACK: 2-> since some of renaming in the same group
03048                                                              //are terminated early
03049                 ifreeL->rtp_stats = ifreeL->stats_t;
03050             }
03051             idcl->stats_t.readAc.access = 3*coredynp.decodeW*coredynp.decodeW*XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_reads;
03052             fdcl->stats_t.readAc.access = 3*coredynp.fp_issueW*coredynp.fp_issueW*XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_rename_writes;
03053             idcl->rtp_stats = idcl->stats_t;
03054             fdcl->rtp_stats = fdcl->stats_t;
03055         }
03056         else
03057         {
03058             if (coredynp.issueW>1)
03059             {
03060                 idcl->stats_t.readAc.access = 2*XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_instructions;
03061                 fdcl->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_instructions;
03062                 idcl->rtp_stats = idcl->stats_t;
03063                 fdcl->rtp_stats = fdcl->stats_t;
03064             }
03065         }
03066 
03067     }
03068     /* Compute engine */
03069     if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03070     {
03071         if (coredynp.scheu_ty==PhysicalRegFile)
03072         {
03073             if (coredynp.rm_ty ==RAMbased)
03074             {
03075                 iFRAT->power_t.reset();
03076                 fFRAT->power_t.reset();
03077 
03078                 iFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03079                         *(iFRAT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic + idcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03080                         +iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*iFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03081                 fFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03082                         *(fFRAT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic + fdcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03083                         +fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*fFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03084             }
03085             else if ((coredynp.rm_ty ==CAMbased))
03086             {
03087                 iFRAT->power_t.reset();
03088                 fFRAT->power_t.reset();
03089                 iFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03090                         *(iFRAT->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic + idcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03091                         +iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*iFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03092                 fFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03093                         *(fFRAT->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic + fdcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03094                         +fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*fFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03095             }
03096 
03097             iRRAT->power_t.reset();
03098             fRRAT->power_t.reset();
03099             ifreeL->power_t.reset();
03100             ffreeL->power_t.reset();
03101 
03102             iRRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (iRRAT->stats_t.readAc.access*iRRAT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic
03103                     +iRRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*iRRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03104             fRRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (fRRAT->stats_t.readAc.access*fRRAT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic
03105                     +fRRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*fRRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03106             ifreeL->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (ifreeL->stats_t.readAc.access*ifreeL->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic
03107                     +ifreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access*ifreeL->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03108             ffreeL->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (ffreeL->stats_t.readAc.access*ffreeL->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic
03109                     +ffreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access*ffreeL->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03110 
03111         }
03112         else if (coredynp.scheu_ty==ReservationStation)
03113         {
03114             if (coredynp.rm_ty ==RAMbased)
03115             {
03116                 iFRAT->power_t.reset();
03117                 fFRAT->power_t.reset();
03118 
03119                 iFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03120                         *(iFRAT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic + idcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03121                         +iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*iFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic
03122                         +iFRAT->stats_t.searchAc.access*iFRAT->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic);
03123                 fFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03124                         *(fFRAT->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic + fdcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03125                         +fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*fFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic
03126                         +fFRAT->stats_t.searchAc.access*fFRAT->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic);
03127             }
03128             else if ((coredynp.rm_ty ==CAMbased))
03129             {
03130                 iFRAT->power_t.reset();
03131                 fFRAT->power_t.reset();
03132                 iFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (iFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03133                         *(iFRAT->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic + idcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03134                         +iFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*iFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03135                 fFRAT->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (fFRAT->stats_t.readAc.access
03136                         *(fFRAT->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic + fdcl->power.readOp.dynamic)
03137                         +fFRAT->stats_t.writeAc.access*fFRAT->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03138             }
03139             ifreeL->power_t.reset();
03140             ifreeL->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  (ifreeL->stats_t.readAc.access*ifreeL->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic
03141                     +ifreeL->stats_t.writeAc.access*ifreeL->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
03142         }
03143 
03144     }
03145     else
03146     {
03147         if (coredynp.issueW>1)
03148         {
03149             idcl->power_t.reset();
03150             fdcl->power_t.reset();
03151             set_pppm(pppm_t, idcl->stats_t.readAc.access, coredynp.num_hthreads, coredynp.num_hthreads, idcl->stats_t.readAc.access);
03152             idcl->power_t = idcl->power * pppm_t;
03153             set_pppm(pppm_t, fdcl->stats_t.readAc.access, coredynp.num_hthreads, coredynp.num_hthreads, idcl->stats_t.readAc.access);
03154             fdcl->power_t = fdcl->power * pppm_t;
03155         }
03156 
03157     }
03158 
03159     //assign value to tpd and rtp
03160     if (is_tdp)
03161     {
03162         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03163         {
03164             if (coredynp.scheu_ty==PhysicalRegFile)
03165             {
03166                 iFRAT->power   =  iFRAT->power_t + (iFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + idcl->power_t;
03167                 fFRAT->power   =  fFRAT->power_t + (fFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + fdcl->power_t;
03168                 iRRAT->power   =  iRRAT->power_t + iRRAT->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03169                 fRRAT->power   =  fRRAT->power_t + fRRAT->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03170                 ifreeL->power  =  ifreeL->power_t + ifreeL->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03171                 ffreeL->power  =  ffreeL->power_t + ffreeL->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03172                 power          =  power + (iFRAT->power + fFRAT->power)
03173                                  + (iRRAT->power + fRRAT->power)
03174                                  + (ifreeL->power + ffreeL->power);
03175             }
03176             else if (coredynp.scheu_ty==ReservationStation)
03177             {
03178                 iFRAT->power   =  iFRAT->power_t + (iFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + idcl->power_t;
03179                 fFRAT->power   =  fFRAT->power_t + (fFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + fdcl->power_t;
03180                 ifreeL->power  =  ifreeL->power_t + ifreeL->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03181                 power          =  power + (iFRAT->power + fFRAT->power)
03182                                  + ifreeL->power;
03183             }
03184         }
03185         else
03186         {
03187             power   =  power + idcl->power_t + fdcl->power_t;
03188         }
03189 
03190     }
03191     else
03192     {
03193         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03194         {
03195             if (coredynp.scheu_ty==PhysicalRegFile)
03196             {
03197                 iFRAT->rt_power   =  iFRAT->power_t + (iFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + idcl->power_t;
03198                 fFRAT->rt_power   =  fFRAT->power_t + (fFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + fdcl->power_t;
03199                 iRRAT->rt_power   =  iRRAT->power_t + iRRAT->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03200                 fRRAT->rt_power   =  fRRAT->power_t + fRRAT->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03201                 ifreeL->rt_power  =  ifreeL->power_t + ifreeL->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03202                 ffreeL->rt_power  =  ffreeL->power_t + ffreeL->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03203                 rt_power          =  rt_power + (iFRAT->rt_power + fFRAT->rt_power)
03204                                    + (iRRAT->rt_power + fRRAT->rt_power)
03205                                    + (ifreeL->rt_power + ffreeL->rt_power);
03206             }
03207             else if (coredynp.scheu_ty==ReservationStation)
03208             {
03209                 iFRAT->rt_power   =  iFRAT->power_t + (iFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + idcl->power_t;
03210                 fFRAT->rt_power   =  fFRAT->power_t + (fFRAT->local_result.power ) * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread + fdcl->power_t;
03211                 ifreeL->rt_power  =  ifreeL->power_t + ifreeL->local_result.power * coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
03212                 rt_power          =  rt_power + (iFRAT->rt_power + fFRAT->rt_power)
03213                                    + ifreeL->rt_power;
03214             }
03215         }
03216         else
03217         {
03218             rt_power   =  rt_power + idcl->power_t + fdcl->power_t;
03219         }
03220 
03221     }
03222 }
03223 
03224 void RENAMINGU::displayEnergy(uint32_t indent,int plevel,bool is_tdp)
03225 {
03226     if (!exist) return;
03227     string indent_str(indent, ' ');
03228     string indent_str_next(indent+2, ' ');
03229     bool long_channel = XML->sys.longer_channel_device;
03230 
03231 
03232     if (is_tdp)
03233     {
03234 
03235         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03236         {
03237             cout << indent_str<< "Int Front End RAT:" << endl;
03238             cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << iFRAT->area.get_area()*1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
03239             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << iFRAT->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
03240             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03241                 << (long_channel? iFRAT->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:iFRAT->power.readOp.leakage) <<" W" << endl;
03242             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << iFRAT->power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
03243             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << iFRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03244             cout <<endl;
03245             cout << indent_str<< "FP Front End RAT:" << endl;
03246             cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << fFRAT->area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
03247             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << fFRAT->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03248             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03249                 << (long_channel? fFRAT->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:fFRAT->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03250             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << fFRAT->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03251             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << fFRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03252             cout <<endl;
03253             cout << indent_str<<"Free List:" << endl;
03254             cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << ifreeL->area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
03255             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << ifreeL->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03256             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03257                 << (long_channel? ifreeL->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:ifreeL->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03258             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << ifreeL->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03259             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << ifreeL->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03260             cout <<endl;
03261 
03262             if (coredynp.scheu_ty==PhysicalRegFile)
03263             {
03264                 cout << indent_str<< "Int Retire RAT: " << endl;
03265                 cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << iRRAT->area.get_area() *1e-6 << " mm^2" << endl;
03266                 cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << iRRAT->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03267                 cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03268                     << (long_channel? iRRAT->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:iRRAT->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03269                 cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << iRRAT->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03270                 cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << iRRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03271                 cout <<endl;
03272                 cout << indent_str<< "FP Retire RAT:" << endl;
03273                 cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << fRRAT->area.get_area()  *1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
03274                 cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << fRRAT->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03275                 cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03276                     << (long_channel? fRRAT->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:fRRAT->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03277                 cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << fRRAT->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03278                 cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << fRRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03279                 cout <<endl;
03280                 cout << indent_str<< "FP Free List:" << endl;
03281                 cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << ffreeL->area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
03282                 cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << ffreeL->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03283                 cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03284                     << (long_channel? ffreeL->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:ffreeL->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03285                 cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << ffreeL->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03286                 cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << ffreeL->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03287                 cout <<endl;
03288             }
03289         }
03290         else
03291         {
03292             cout << indent_str<< "Int DCL:" << endl;
03293             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << idcl->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03294             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03295                 << (long_channel? idcl->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:idcl->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03296             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << idcl->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03297             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << idcl->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03298             cout << indent_str<<"FP DCL:" << endl;
03299             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << fdcl->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03300             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03301                 << (long_channel? fdcl->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:fdcl->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03302             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << fdcl->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03303             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << fdcl->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03304         }
03305     }
03306     else
03307     {
03308         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03309         {
03310             cout << indent_str_next << "Int Front End RAT    Peak Dynamic = " << iFRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
03311             cout << indent_str_next << "Int Front End RAT    Subthreshold Leakage = " << iFRAT->rt_power.readOp.leakage <<" W" << endl;
03312             cout << indent_str_next << "Int Front End RAT    Gate Leakage = " << iFRAT->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
03313             cout << indent_str_next << "FP Front End RAT   Peak Dynamic = " << fFRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03314             cout << indent_str_next << "FP Front End RAT   Subthreshold Leakage = " << fFRAT->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03315             cout << indent_str_next << "FP Front End RAT   Gate Leakage = " << fFRAT->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03316             cout << indent_str_next << "Free List   Peak Dynamic = " << ifreeL->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03317             cout << indent_str_next << "Free List   Subthreshold Leakage = " << ifreeL->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03318             cout << indent_str_next << "Free List   Gate Leakage = " << fFRAT->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03319             if (coredynp.scheu_ty==PhysicalRegFile)
03320             {
03321                 cout << indent_str_next << "Int Retire RAT   Peak Dynamic = " << iRRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03322                 cout << indent_str_next << "Int Retire RAT   Subthreshold Leakage = " << iRRAT->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03323                 cout << indent_str_next << "Int Retire RAT   Gate Leakage = " << iRRAT->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03324                 cout << indent_str_next << "FP Retire RAT   Peak Dynamic = " << fRRAT->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03325                 cout << indent_str_next << "FP Retire RAT   Subthreshold Leakage = " << fRRAT->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03326                 cout << indent_str_next << "FP Retire RAT   Gate Leakage = " << fRRAT->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03327                 cout << indent_str_next << "FP Free List   Peak Dynamic = " << ffreeL->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03328                 cout << indent_str_next << "FP Free List   Subthreshold Leakage = " << ffreeL->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03329                 cout << indent_str_next << "FP Free List   Gate Leakage = " << fFRAT->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03330             }
03331         }
03332         else
03333         {
03334             cout << indent_str_next << "Int DCL   Peak Dynamic = " << idcl->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03335             cout << indent_str_next << "Int DCL   Subthreshold Leakage = " << idcl->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03336             cout << indent_str_next << "Int DCL   Gate Leakage = " << idcl->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03337             cout << indent_str_next << "FP DCL   Peak Dynamic = " << fdcl->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03338             cout << indent_str_next << "FP DCL   Subthreshold Leakage = " << fdcl->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03339             cout << indent_str_next << "FP DCL   Gate Leakage = " << fdcl->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03340         }
03341     }
03342 
03343 }
03344 
03345 
03346 void SchedulerU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
03347 {
03348     if (!exist) return;
03349     double ROB_duty_cycle;
03350 //  ROB_duty_cycle = ((coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle + coredynp.num_muls>0?coredynp.MUL_duty_cycle:0
03351 //          + coredynp.num_fpus>0?coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle:0))*1.1<1 ? (coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle + coredynp.num_muls>0?coredynp.MUL_duty_cycle:0
03352 //                  + coredynp.num_fpus>0?coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle:0)*1.1:1;
03353     ROB_duty_cycle = 1;
03354     //init stats
03355     if (is_tdp)
03356     {
03357         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03358         {
03359             int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access    = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03360             int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access   = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
03361             int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access  = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;
03362             int_inst_window->tdp_stats                = int_inst_window->stats_t;
03363             fp_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access     = fp_inst_window->l_ip.num_rd_ports*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
03364             fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access    = fp_inst_window->l_ip.num_wr_ports*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
03365             fp_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access   = fp_inst_window->l_ip.num_search_ports*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
03366             fp_inst_window->tdp_stats                 = fp_inst_window->stats_t;
03367 
03368             if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
03369             {
03370                 ROB->stats_t.readAc.access   = coredynp.commitW*coredynp.num_pipelines*ROB_duty_cycle;
03371                 ROB->stats_t.writeAc.access  = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines*ROB_duty_cycle;
03372                 ROB->tdp_stats        = ROB->stats_t;
03373 
03374                 /*
03375                  * When inst commits, ROB must be read.
03376                  * Because for Physcial register based cores, physical register tag in ROB
03377                  * need to be read out and write into RRAT/CAM based RAT.
03378                  * For RS based cores, register content that stored in ROB must be
03379                  * read out and stored in architectural registers.
03380                  *
03381                  * if no-register is involved, the ROB read out operation when instruction commits can be ignored.
03382                  * assuming 20% insts. belong this type.
03383                  * TODO: ROB duty_cycle need to be revisited
03384                  */
03385             }
03386 
03387         }
03388         else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
03389         {
03390             int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access   = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03391             int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access  = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
03392             int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;
03393             int_inst_window->tdp_stats       = int_inst_window->stats_t;
03394         }
03395 
03396      }
03397     else
03398     {//rtp
03399         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03400         {
03401             int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].inst_window_reads;
03402             int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].inst_window_writes;
03403             int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].inst_window_wakeup_accesses;
03404             int_inst_window->rtp_stats               = int_inst_window->stats_t;
03405             fp_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_inst_window_reads;
03406             fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_inst_window_writes;
03407             fp_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_inst_window_wakeup_accesses;
03408             fp_inst_window->rtp_stats                = fp_inst_window->stats_t;
03409 
03410             if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
03411             {
03412 
03413                 ROB->stats_t.readAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_reads;
03414                 ROB->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_writes;
03415                 /* ROB need to be updated in RS based OOO when new values are produced,
03416                  * this update may happen before the commit stage when ROB entry is released
03417                  * 1. ROB write at instruction inserted in
03418                  * 2. ROB write as results produced (for RS based OOO only)
03419                  * 3. ROB read  as instruction committed. For RS based OOO, data values are read out and sent to ARF
03420                  * For Physical reg based OOO, no data stored in ROB, but register tags need to be
03421                  * read out and used to set the RRAT and to recycle the register tag to free list buffer
03422                  */
03423                 ROB->rtp_stats        = ROB->stats_t;
03424             }
03425 
03426         }
03427         else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
03428         {
03429             int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_instructions + XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_instructions;
03430             int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access   = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_instructions + XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_instructions;
03431             int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access  = 2*(XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_instructions + XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_instructions);
03432             int_inst_window->rtp_stats                = int_inst_window->stats_t;
03433         }
03434     }
03435 
03436     //computation engine
03437     if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03438     {
03439         int_inst_window->power_t.reset();
03440         fp_inst_window->power_t.reset();
03441 
03442         /* each instruction needs to write to scheduler, read out when all resources and source operands are ready
03443          * two search ops with one for each source operand
03444          *
03445          */
03446         int_inst_window->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  int_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access
03447                     + int_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access
03448                     + int_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic  * int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access
03449                     + int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access * instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic;
03450 
03451         fp_inst_window->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  fp_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic * fp_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access
03452                     + fp_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * fp_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access
03453                     + fp_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic * fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access
03454                     + fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access * instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic;
03455 
03456         if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
03457         {
03458             ROB->power_t.reset();
03459             ROB->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  ROB->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*ROB->stats_t.readAc.access +
03460                         ROB->stats_t.writeAc.access*ROB->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03461         }
03462 
03463 
03464 
03465 
03466     }
03467     else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
03468     {
03469         int_inst_window->power_t.reset();
03470         int_inst_window->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  int_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access
03471                           + int_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access
03472                           + int_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic  * int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access
03473                           + int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access * instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic;
03474     }
03475 
03476     //assign values
03477     if (is_tdp)
03478     {
03479         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03480         {
03481             int_inst_window->power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
03482             fp_inst_window->power = fp_inst_window->power_t + (fp_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
03483             power      = power + int_inst_window->power + fp_inst_window->power;
03484             if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
03485             {
03486                 ROB->power = ROB->power_t + ROB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
03487                 power      = power + ROB->power;
03488             }
03489 
03490         }
03491         else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
03492         {
03493             //          set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].issue_width,1, 1, 1);
03494             int_inst_window->power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
03495             power      = power + int_inst_window->power;
03496         }
03497 
03498      }
03499     else
03500     {//rtp
03501         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03502         {
03503             int_inst_window->rt_power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
03504             fp_inst_window->rt_power  = fp_inst_window->power_t + (fp_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
03505             rt_power                  = rt_power + int_inst_window->rt_power + fp_inst_window->rt_power;
03506             if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
03507             {
03508                 ROB->rt_power = ROB->power_t + ROB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
03509                 rt_power                  = rt_power + ROB->rt_power;
03510             }
03511 
03512         }
03513         else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
03514         {
03515             //          set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].issue_width,1, 1, 1);
03516             int_inst_window->rt_power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
03517             rt_power                  = rt_power + int_inst_window->rt_power;
03518         }
03519     }
03520 //  set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].issue_width,1, 1, 1);
03521 //  cout<<"Scheduler power="<<power.readOp.dynamic<<"leakage="<<power.readOp.leakage<<endl;
03522 //  cout<<"IW="<<int_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access +
03523 //    + int_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access<<"leakage="<<int_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.leakage<<endl;
03524 //  cout<<"selection"<<instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic<<"leakage"<<instruction_selection->power.readOp.leakage<<endl;
03525 }
03526 
03527 void SchedulerU::displayEnergy(uint32_t indent,int plevel,bool is_tdp)
03528 {
03529     if (!exist) return;
03530     string indent_str(indent, ' ');
03531     string indent_str_next(indent+2, ' ');
03532     bool long_channel = XML->sys.longer_channel_device;
03533 
03534 
03535     if (is_tdp)
03536     {
03537         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03538         {
03539             cout << indent_str << "Instruction Window:" << endl;
03540             cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << int_inst_window->area.get_area()*1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
03541             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << int_inst_window->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
03542             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03543                 << (long_channel? int_inst_window->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:int_inst_window->power.readOp.leakage) <<" W" << endl;
03544             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << int_inst_window->power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
03545             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03546             cout <<endl;
03547             cout << indent_str << "FP Instruction Window:" << endl;
03548             cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << fp_inst_window->area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
03549             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << fp_inst_window->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03550             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03551                 << (long_channel? fp_inst_window->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:fp_inst_window->power.readOp.leakage ) << " W" << endl;
03552             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << fp_inst_window->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03553             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << fp_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03554             cout <<endl;
03555             if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
03556             {
03557                 cout << indent_str<<"ROB:" << endl;
03558                 cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << ROB->area.get_area() *1e-6 << " mm^2" << endl;
03559                 cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << ROB->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03560                 cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03561                 << (long_channel? ROB->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:ROB->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
03562                 cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << ROB->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03563                 cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << ROB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03564                 cout <<endl;
03565             }
03566         }
03567         else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
03568         {
03569             cout << indent_str << "Instruction Window:" << endl;
03570             cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << int_inst_window->area.get_area()*1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
03571             cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << int_inst_window->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
03572             cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
03573                 << (long_channel? int_inst_window->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:int_inst_window->power.readOp.leakage) <<" W" << endl;
03574             cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << int_inst_window->power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
03575             cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
03576             cout <<endl;
03577         }
03578     }
03579     else
03580     {
03581         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
03582         {
03583             cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Window    Peak Dynamic = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
03584             cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Window    Subthreshold Leakage = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.leakage <<" W" << endl;
03585             cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Window    Gate Leakage = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
03586             cout << indent_str_next << "FP Instruction Window   Peak Dynamic = " << fp_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03587             cout << indent_str_next << "FP Instruction Window   Subthreshold Leakage = " << fp_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03588             cout << indent_str_next << "FP Instruction Window   Gate Leakage = " << fp_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03589             if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
03590             {
03591                 cout << indent_str_next << "ROB   Peak Dynamic = " << ROB->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
03592                 cout << indent_str_next << "ROB   Subthreshold Leakage = " << ROB->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
03593                 cout << indent_str_next << "ROB   Gate Leakage = " << ROB->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
03594             }
03595         }
03596         else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
03597         {
03598             cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Window    Peak Dynamic = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
03599             cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Window    Subthreshold Leakage = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.leakage <<" W" << endl;
03600             cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Window    Gate Leakage = " << int_inst_window->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
03601         }
03602     }
03603
