03605 
03606 void LoadStoreU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
03607 {
03608     if (!exist) return;
03609 
03610     executionTime=XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6);//Syed
03611 
03612     //RF crossbar power (Syed)
03613     xbar_shared->compute_power();
03614    
03615     if (is_tdp)
03616         {
03617 
03618             //init stats for Peak
03619         // added by Jingwen
03620             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.access  = 0.67*sharedmemory.caches->l_ip.num_rw_ports*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle;
03621             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss    = 0;
03622             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit     = sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.access - sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
03623             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.access = 0.33*sharedmemory.caches->l_ip.num_rw_ports*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle;
03624             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss   = 0;
03625             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.hit    = sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.access - sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss;
03626             sharedmemory.caches->tdp_stats = sharedmemory.caches->stats_t;
03627 
03628             sharedmemory.missb->stats_t.readAc.access  = sharedmemory.missb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03629             sharedmemory.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access = sharedmemory.missb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03630             sharedmemory.missb->tdp_stats = sharedmemory.missb->stats_t;
03631 
03632             sharedmemory.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access  = sharedmemory.ifb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03633             sharedmemory.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access = sharedmemory.ifb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03634             sharedmemory.ifb->tdp_stats = sharedmemory.ifb->stats_t;
03635 
03636             sharedmemory.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access  = sharedmemory.prefetchb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03637             sharedmemory.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access = sharedmemory.ifb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03638             sharedmemory.prefetchb->tdp_stats = sharedmemory.prefetchb->stats_t;
03639             if (cache_p==Write_back)
03640             {
03641                 sharedmemory.wbb->stats_t.readAc.access  = sharedmemory.wbb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03642                 sharedmemory.wbb->stats_t.writeAc.access = sharedmemory.wbb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
03643                 sharedmemory.wbb->tdp_stats = sharedmemory.wbb->stats_t;
03644             }
03645 
03646 
03647 
03648             //init stats for Peak
03649             dcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.access  = 0.67*dcache.caches->l_ip.num_rw_ports*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle;
03650             dcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss    = 0;

03899 
03900     sharedmemory.power_t.readOp.dynamic += (sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit*sharedmemory.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03901             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss*sharedmemory.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03902             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*sharedmemory.caches->local_result.tag_array2->power.readOp.dynamic+
03903             sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.access*sharedmemory.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic +
03904             xbar_shared->power.readOp.dynamic*(sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit+ sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.hit));
03905 
03906 
03907     dcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   += (dcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit*dcache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03908             dcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss*dcache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03909             dcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*dcache.caches->local_result.tag_array2->power.readOp.dynamic+
03910             dcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.access*dcache.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic +
03911             xbar_shared->power.readOp.dynamic*(dcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit+ dcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.hit));
03912     ccache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   += (ccache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit*ccache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03913             ccache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss*ccache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03914             ccache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*ccache.caches->local_result.tag_array2->power.readOp.dynamic+
03915             ccache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.access*ccache.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic + 
03916             xbar_shared->power.readOp.dynamic*(ccache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit));
03917 
03918     tcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   += (tcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit*tcache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03919             tcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss*tcache.caches->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic+
03920             tcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*tcache.caches->local_result.tag_array2->power.readOp.dynamic+
03921             tcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.access*tcache.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic+
03922             xbar_shared->power.readOp.dynamic*(tcache.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit+ tcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.hit));
03923 
03924     if (cache_p==Write_back)
03925     {//write miss will generate a write later
03926         dcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   += dcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*dcache.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03927         ccache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   += ccache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*ccache.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03928         tcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   += tcache.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*tcache.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03929         sharedmemory.power_t.readOp.dynamic += sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.miss*sharedmemory.caches->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03930     }
03931 
03932 
03933     sharedmemory.power_t.readOp.dynamic +=  sharedmemory.missb->stats_t.readAc.access*sharedmemory.missb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03934             sharedmemory.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access*sharedmemory.missb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//each access to missb involves a CAM and a write
03935     sharedmemory.power_t.readOp.dynamic +=  sharedmemory.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access*sharedmemory.ifb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03936             sharedmemory.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access*sharedmemory.ifb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03937     sharedmemory.power_t.readOp.dynamic +=  sharedmemory.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access*sharedmemory.prefetchb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03938             sharedmemory.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access*sharedmemory.prefetchb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03939     if (cache_p==Write_back)
03940     {
03941         sharedmemory.power_t.readOp.dynamic +=  sharedmemory.wbb->stats_t.readAc.access*sharedmemory.wbb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic
03942             + sharedmemory.wbb->stats_t.writeAc.access*sharedmemory.wbb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03943     }
03944 
03945 
03946     dcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  dcache.missb->stats_t.readAc.access*dcache.missb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03947             dcache.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access*dcache.missb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//each access to missb involves a CAM and a write
03948     dcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  dcache.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access*dcache.ifb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03949             dcache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access*dcache.ifb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03950     dcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  dcache.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access*dcache.prefetchb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03951             dcache.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access*dcache.prefetchb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03952     if (cache_p==Write_back)
03953     {
03954         dcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  dcache.wbb->stats_t.readAc.access*dcache.wbb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic
03955             + dcache.wbb->stats_t.writeAc.access*dcache.wbb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03956     }
03957 
03958     ccache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  ccache.missb->stats_t.readAc.access*ccache.missb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03959             ccache.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access*ccache.missb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//each access to missb involves a CAM and a write
03960     ccache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  ccache.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access*ccache.ifb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03961             ccache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access*ccache.ifb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03962     ccache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  ccache.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access*ccache.prefetchb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03963             ccache.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access*ccache.prefetchb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03964     if (cache_p==Write_back)
03965     {
03966         ccache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  ccache.wbb->stats_t.readAc.access*ccache.wbb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic
03967             + ccache.wbb->stats_t.writeAc.access*ccache.wbb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03968     }
03969 
03970     tcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  tcache.missb->stats_t.readAc.access*tcache.missb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03971             tcache.missb->stats_t.writeAc.access*tcache.missb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//each access to missb involves a CAM and a write
03972     tcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  tcache.ifb->stats_t.readAc.access*tcache.ifb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03973             tcache.ifb->stats_t.writeAc.access*tcache.ifb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03974     tcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  tcache.prefetchb->stats_t.readAc.access*tcache.prefetchb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic +
03975             tcache.prefetchb->stats_t.writeAc.access*tcache.prefetchb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03976     if (cache_p==Write_back)
03977     {
03978         tcache.power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  tcache.wbb->stats_t.readAc.access*tcache.wbb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic
03979             + tcache.wbb->stats_t.writeAc.access*tcache.wbb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
03980     }
03981 
03982 
03983     if ((coredynp.core_ty==OOO) && (XML->sys.core[ithCore].load_buffer_size >0))
03984     {
03985         LoadQ->power_t.reset();
03986         LoadQ->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  LoadQ->stats_t.readAc.access*(LoadQ->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic+ LoadQ->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic)+
03987                 LoadQ->stats_t.writeAc.access*LoadQ->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//every memory access invloves at least two operations on LoadQ
03988 
03989         LSQ->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  LSQ->stats_t.readAc.access*(LSQ->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic + LSQ->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic)
03990                     + LSQ->stats_t.writeAc.access*LSQ->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//every memory access invloves at least two operations on LSQ
03991 
03992     }
03993     else
03994     {
03995     //  LSQ->power_t.readOp.dynamic  +=  LSQ->stats_t.readAc.access*(LSQ->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic + LSQ->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic)
03996         //          + LSQ->stats_t.writeAc.access*LSQ->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;//every memory access invloves at least two operations on LSQ
03997         //  No LSQ in GPUs (Syed)
03998 
03999     }
04000 
04001     if (is_tdp)
04002     {
04003 //      dcache.power = dcache.power_t + (dcache.caches->local_result.power)*pppm_lkg +
04004 //              (dcache.missb->local_result.power +
04005 //              dcache.ifb->local_result.power +
04006 //              dcache.prefetchb->local_result.power +
04007 //              dcache.wbb->local_result.power)*pppm_Isub;
04008 
04009 
04010         sharedmemory.power = sharedmemory.power_t + (sharedmemory.caches->local_result.power +
04011                 sharedmemory.missb->local_result.power +
04012                 sharedmemory.ifb->local_result.power +
04013                 sharedmemory.prefetchb->local_result.power + xbar_shared->power) *pppm_lkg;
04014         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04015         {
04016             sharedmemory.power = sharedmemory.power + sharedmemory.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04017         }
04018 
04019 
04020         dcache.power = dcache.power_t + (dcache.caches->local_result.power +
04021                 dcache.missb->local_result.power +
04022                 dcache.ifb->local_result.power +
04023                 dcache.prefetchb->local_result.power) *pppm_lkg;
04024         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04025         {
04026             dcache.power = dcache.power + dcache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04027         }
04028 
04029         ccache.power = ccache.power_t + (ccache.caches->local_result.power +
04030                 ccache.missb->local_result.power +
04031                 ccache.ifb->local_result.power +
04032                 ccache.prefetchb->local_result.power) *pppm_lkg;
04033         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04034         {
04035             ccache.power = ccache.power + ccache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04036         }
04037 
04038         tcache.power = tcache.power_t + (tcache.caches->local_result.power +
04039                 tcache.missb->local_result.power +
04040                 tcache.ifb->local_result.power +
04041                 tcache.prefetchb->local_result.power) *pppm_lkg;
04042         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04043         {
04044             tcache.power = tcache.power + tcache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04045         }
04046 
04047 
04048         LSQ->power = LSQ->power_t + LSQ->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04049         //No LSQ in GPUs (Syed)
04050     LSQ->power.reset();
04051         power     = power + dcache.power + LSQ->power +sharedmemory.power + ccache.power + tcache.power;
04052 
04053         if ((coredynp.core_ty==OOO) && (XML->sys.core[ithCore].load_buffer_size >0))
04054         {
04055             LoadQ->power = LoadQ->power_t + LoadQ->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04056             power     = power + LoadQ->power;
04057         }
04058     }
04059     else
04060     {
04061 //      dcache.rt_power = dcache.power_t + (dcache.caches->local_result.power +
04062 //              dcache.missb->local_result.power +
04063 //              dcache.ifb->local_result.power +
04064 //              dcache.prefetchb->local_result.power +
04065 //              dcache.wbb->local_result.power)*pppm_lkg;
04066       rt_power.reset();
04067       sharedmemory.rt_power.reset(); //Jingwen
04068       tcache.rt_power.reset();
04069       ccache.rt_power.reset();
04070       dcache.rt_power.reset();
04071       LSQ->rt_power.reset();
04072 
04073 
04074         sharedmemory.rt_power = sharedmemory.power_t + (sharedmemory.caches->local_result.power +
04075                 sharedmemory.missb->local_result.power +
04076                 sharedmemory.ifb->local_result.power +
04077                 sharedmemory.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
04078 
04079         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04080         {
04081             sharedmemory.rt_power = sharedmemory.rt_power + sharedmemory.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04082         }
04083 
04084         dcache.rt_power = dcache.power_t + (dcache.caches->local_result.power +
04085                 dcache.missb->local_result.power +
04086                 dcache.ifb->local_result.power +
04087                 dcache.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
04088         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04089         {
04090             dcache.rt_power = dcache.rt_power + dcache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04091         }
04092 
04093         ccache.rt_power = ccache.power_t + (ccache.caches->local_result.power +
04094                 ccache.missb->local_result.power +
04095                 ccache.ifb->local_result.power +
04096                 ccache.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
04097         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04098         {
04099             ccache.rt_power = ccache.rt_power + ccache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04100         }
04101 
04102         tcache.rt_power = tcache.power_t + (tcache.caches->local_result.power +
04103                 tcache.missb->local_result.power +
04104                 tcache.ifb->local_result.power +
04105                 tcache.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
04106         if (cache_p==Write_back)
04107         {
04108             tcache.rt_power = tcache.rt_power + tcache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04109         }
04110 
04111 
04112 
04113         LSQ->rt_power = LSQ->power_t + LSQ->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04114         LSQ->rt_power.reset();
04115         rt_power     = rt_power + dcache.rt_power + LSQ->rt_power + sharedmemory.rt_power + ccache.rt_power + tcache.rt_power;
04116 
04117         if ((coredynp.core_ty==OOO) && (XML->sys.core[ithCore].load_buffer_size >0))
04118         {
04119             LoadQ->rt_power = LoadQ->power_t + LoadQ->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04120             rt_power     = rt_power + LoadQ->rt_power;
04121         }
04122     }
04123 }

04250 
04251 void MemManU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
04252 {
04253 
04254     if (!exist) return;
04255     if (is_tdp)
04256     {
04257         //init stats for Peak
04258         itlb->stats_t.readAc.access  = itlb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
04259         itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss    = 0;
04260         itlb->stats_t.readAc.hit     = itlb->stats_t.readAc.access - itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
04261         itlb->tdp_stats = itlb->stats_t;
04262 
04263         dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access  = dtlb->l_ip.num_search_ports*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle;
04264         dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss    = 0;
04265         dtlb->stats_t.readAc.hit     = dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access - dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
04266         dtlb->tdp_stats = dtlb->stats_t;
04267      }
04268     else
04269     {
04270         //init stats for Runtime Dynamic (RTP)
04271         itlb->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].itlb.total_accesses;
04272         itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].itlb.total_misses;
04273         itlb->stats_t.readAc.hit     = itlb->stats_t.readAc.access - itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
04274         itlb->rtp_stats = itlb->stats_t;
04275 
04276         dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].dtlb.total_accesses;
04277         dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss    = XML->sys.core[ithCore].dtlb.total_misses;
04278         dtlb->stats_t.readAc.hit     = dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access - dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
04279         dtlb->rtp_stats = dtlb->stats_t;
04280     }
04281 
04282     itlb->power_t.reset();
04283     dtlb->power_t.reset();
04284     itlb->power_t.readOp.dynamic +=  itlb->stats_t.readAc.access*itlb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic//FA spent most power in tag, so use total access not hits
04285                           +itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss*itlb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
04286     dtlb->power_t.readOp.dynamic +=  dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access*dtlb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic//FA spent most power in tag, so use total access not hits
04287                           +dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss*dtlb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
04288 
04289     if (is_tdp)
04290         {
04291         itlb->power = itlb->power_t + itlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04292         dtlb->power = dtlb->power_t + dtlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04293         power     = power + itlb->power + dtlb->power;
04294         }
04295         else
04296         {
04297             itlb->rt_power = itlb->power_t + itlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04298             dtlb->rt_power = dtlb->power_t + dtlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04299             rt_power     = rt_power + itlb->rt_power + dtlb->rt_power;
04300         }
04301 
04302 }
04303 
04304 void MemManU::displayEnergy(uint32_t indent,int plevel,bool is_tdp)
04305 {
04306     if (!exist) return;
04307     string indent_str(indent, ' ');
04308     string indent_str_next(indent+2, ' ');
04309     bool long_channel = XML->sys.longer_channel_device;
04310 
04311 
04312 
04313 
04314     if (is_tdp)
04315     {
04316         cout << indent_str << "Itlb:" << endl;
04317         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << itlb->area.get_area()*1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
04318         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << itlb->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
04319         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "

04326         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << dtlb->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04327         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
04328             << (long_channel? dtlb->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:dtlb->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
04329         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << dtlb->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
04330         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << dtlb->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
04331         cout <<endl;
04332     }
04333     else
04334     {
04335         cout << indent_str_next << "Itlb    Peak Dynamic = " << itlb->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
04336         cout << indent_str_next << "Itlb    Subthreshold Leakage = " << itlb->rt_power.readOp.leakage <<" W" << endl;
04337         cout << indent_str_next << "Itlb    Gate Leakage = " << itlb->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
04338         cout << indent_str_next << "Dtlb   Peak Dynamic = " << dtlb->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04339         cout << indent_str_next << "Dtlb   Subthreshold Leakage = " << dtlb->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
04340         cout << indent_str_next << "Dtlb   Gate Leakage = " << dtlb->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
04341     }
04342 
04343 }
04344 
04345 void RegFU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
04346 {
04347 /*
04348  * Architecture RF and physical RF cannot be present at the same time.
04349  * Therefore, the RF stats can only refer to either ARF or PRF;
04350  * And the same stats can be used for both.
04351  */
04352     if (!exist) return;
04353 
04354   executionTime=XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6);//Syed
04355  //RF crossbar power (Syed Gilani)
04356  xbar_rfu->compute_power();
04357 
04358 
04359  //Arbiter power
04360  arbiter_rfu->compute_power(); 
04361 
04362     if (is_tdp)
04363     {
04364         //RF power -- modified by Syed
04365         //init stats for Peak
04366 
04367         IRF->stats_t.readAc.access  = 4;
04368         IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 4;
04369         IRF->tdp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
04370 
04371         IRF->stats_t.readAc.access  = 2;
04372         IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 1;
04373         IRF->tdp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
04374 
04375 
04376         OPC->stats_t.readAc.access  = 32;
04377         OPC->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 32;
04378         OPC->tdp_stats = OPC->stats_t;
04379 
04380         //Commented by Syed (GPUs have a single RF which we model by IRF)
04381         //FRF->stats_t.readAc.access  = FRF->l_ip.num_rd_ports*coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle*1.05*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
04382         //FRF->stats_t.writeAc.access  = FRF->l_ip.num_wr_ports*coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle*1.05*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
04383         //FRF->tdp_stats = FRF->stats_t;
04384         if (coredynp.regWindowing)
04385         {
04386             RFWIN->stats_t.readAc.access  = 0;//0.5*RFWIN->l_ip.num_rw_ports;
04387             RFWIN->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 0;//0.5*RFWIN->l_ip.num_rw_ports;
04388             RFWIN->tdp_stats = RFWIN->stats_t;
04389         }
04390      } /* if (is_tdp) */ 
04391     else
04392     {
04393         //init stats for Runtime Dynamic (RTP)
04394         //in Tesla each RF operand accesses 2 banks, so multiply acceses by 2
04395         // (read and write energies of reg_file are per bank)(Tesla) : Syed
04396         // Also, for a SIMD width of 8 and warp size of 32 threads, 4 accesses
04397         // (each accessing 2 banks) need to be performed per operand
04398 if (XML->sys.architecture==1){
04399         IRF->stats_t.readAc.access  = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/32)*(4*2);
04400         IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access  = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_writes/32)*(4*2);
04401 } else {
04402         IRF->stats_t.readAc.access  = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/32)*(2*4);
04403         IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access  = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_writes/32)*(2*4);
04404 }
04405         IRF->rtp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
04406 
04407         OPC->stats_t.readAc.access  = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads)/*/1.5*/+XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands;
04408         OPC->stats_t.writeAc.access  = 0;
04409         OPC->rtp_stats = OPC->stats_t;
04410 
04411       //cout<< "IRF read energy: "<<    IRF->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic<<endl;
04412       //cout<< "IRF write energy: "<<    IRF->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic<<endl;
04413         //FRF->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].float_regfile_reads;
04414         //FRF->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].float_regfile_writes;
04415         //FRF->rtp_stats = FRF->stats_t;
04416         if (coredynp.regWindowing)
04417         {
04418             RFWIN->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
04419             RFWIN->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
04420             RFWIN->rtp_stats = RFWIN->stats_t;
04421 
04422             IRF->stats_t.readAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads +
04423                  XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
04424             IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access  = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_writes +
04425                  XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
04426             IRF->rtp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
04427 
04428         }
04429     }
04430     IRF->power_t.reset();
04431     FRF->power_t.reset();
04432     OPC->power_t.reset();
04433     //IRF->power_t  =  IRF->power_t + IRF->local_result.power;// + xbar_rfu->power + arbiter_rfu->power;
04434 
04435 
04436     
04437     IRF->power_t.readOp.dynamic  =  (IRF->stats_t.readAc.access*IRF->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic
04438             +IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access*IRF->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
04439     OPC->power_t.readOp.dynamic  =  (OPC->stats_t.readAc.access*OPC->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic);
04440 
04441     if (coredynp.regWindowing)
04442     {
04443         RFWIN->power_t.reset();
04444         RFWIN->power_t.readOp.dynamic   +=  (RFWIN->stats_t.readAc.access*RFWIN->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic +
04445                 RFWIN->stats_t.writeAc.access*RFWIN->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
04446     }
04447 
04448     if (is_tdp)
04449     {
04450 
04451         //cout<<"pre: IRF_power_t: "<<IRF->power.readOp.dynamic<<" ("<<IRF->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate<<") "<<" IRF_localresult: "<<
04452          //                   IRF->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic<<endl;
04453         //Syed: removed the multiplication of power by hardware threads
04454         //since the one IRF  is shared by all threads in GPUs
04455 
04456         //FRF->power  =  FRF->power_t + FRF->local_result.power *coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
04457 
04458       double pppm_lkg_banks[4];
04459       set_pppm(pppm_lkg_banks, 0,XML->sys.core[ithCore].collector_units,XML->sys.core[ithCore].collector_units );
04460       IRF->power = (IRF->power_t) + IRF->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04461       IRF->power.readOp.dynamic=IRF->power_t.readOp.dynamic*1;
04462       OPC->power = (OPC->power_t) + OPC->local_result.power *pppm_lkg_banks;
04463       OPC->power.readOp.dynamic=OPC->power_t.readOp.dynamic*1;
04464 
04465       
04466       power     =  power + (IRF->power+OPC->power);
04467 
04468 
04469         if (coredynp.regWindowing)
04470         {
04471             RFWIN->power = RFWIN->power_t + RFWIN->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04472             power        = power + RFWIN->power;
04473         }
04474     } /* if (is_tdp) */ 
04475     else
04476     {
04477       //Removed *coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread since all hardware threads shared the same IRF
04478         IRF->rt_power  =  IRF->power_t + IRF->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;/* *coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;*/
04479         OPC->rt_power = OPC->power_t +  OPC->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
04480 if(XML->sys.architecture==1){
04481     //Each warp operand accesses the crossbar
04482    xbar_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic=((XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/(32))+(XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands/(32)))*xbar_rfu->power.readOp.dynamic;
04483 } else {
04484     xbar_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic=((XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/(32))+(XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands/(32)))*xbar_rfu->power.readOp.dynamic;
04485 }
04486         arbiter_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic=((XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/(32))+(XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands/(32)))*arbiter_rfu->power.readOp.dynamic;
04487 
04488 
04489         rt_power       =  rt_power + (IRF->power_t /*+ FRF->power_t*/+xbar_rfu->rt_power+arbiter_rfu->rt_power+OPC->power_t);
04490         if (coredynp.regWindowing)
04491         {
04492             RFWIN->rt_power = RFWIN->power_t + RFWIN->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
04493             rt_power        = rt_power + RFWIN->rt_power;
04494         }
04495     }
04496 }
04497

04523         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << xbar_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
04524         cout <<endl;
04525       
04526         cout << indent_str << "Arbiter (Integer RF):" << endl;
04527         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << arbiter_rfu->area.get_area()*1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
04528         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << arbiter_rfu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
04529         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
04530             << (long_channel? arbiter_rfu->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:arbiter_rfu->power.readOp.leakage) <<" W" << endl;
04531 
04532         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << arbiter_rfu->power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
04533         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << arbiter_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
04534         cout <<endl;
04535 
04536         /*
04537         cout << indent_str<< "Floating Point RF:" << endl;
04538         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << FRF->area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
04539         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << FRF->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04540         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
04541             << (long_channel? FRF->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:FRF->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
04542         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << FRF->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
04543         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << FRF->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
04544         cout <<endl;
04545         */

04547         {
04548             cout << indent_str << "Register Windows:" << endl;

04574 
04575 
04576 void EXECU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
04577 {
04578     if (!exist) return;
04579     //Syed
04580     double pppm_t[4]    = {1,1,1,1};
04581     double pppm_freqScaling[4]    = {rf_fu_clockRate/clockRate,1,1,1};
04582   executionTime=XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6);//Syed
04583 
04584 
04585 //  rfu->power.reset();
04586   rfu->rt_power.reset();
04587 //  scheu->power.reset();
04588     scheu->rt_power.reset();
04589 //  exeu->power.reset();
04590     exeu->rt_power.reset();
04591 
04592     rfu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04593     scheu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04594     exeu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04595     if (coredynp.num_fpus >0)
04596     {
04597     fp_u->rt_power.reset();
04598         fp_u->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04599     }
04600     if (coredynp.num_muls >0)
04601     {
04602     mul->rt_power.reset();
04603         mul->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04604     }
04605   bypass.rt_power.reset();
04606 
04607     if (is_tdp)
04608     {
04609         set_pppm(pppm_t, 2*coredynp.ALU_cdb_duty_cycle, 2, 2, 2*coredynp.ALU_cdb_duty_cycle);//2 means two source operands needs to be passed for each int instruction.
04610         //bypass.power = bypass.power + intTagBypass->power*pppm_t + int_bypass->power*pppm_t;
04611         if (coredynp.num_muls >0)
04612         {
04613             set_pppm(pppm_t, 2*coredynp.MUL_cdb_duty_cycle, 2, 2, 2*coredynp.MUL_cdb_duty_cycle);//2 means two source operands needs to be passed for each int instruction.
04614             //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)
04615             //bypass.power = bypass.power + intTag_mul_Bypass->power*pppm_t + int_mul_bypass->power*pppm_t;
04616             power      = power + mul->power*pppm_freqScaling;
04617         }
04618 
04619         if (coredynp.num_fpus>0)
04620         {
04621             set_pppm(pppm_t, 3*coredynp.FPU_cdb_duty_cycle, 3, 3, 3*coredynp.FPU_cdb_duty_cycle);//3 means three source operands needs to be passed for each fp instruction.
04622             //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)           
04623             //bypass.power = bypass.power + fp_bypass->power*pppm_t  + fpTagBypass->power*pppm_t ;
04624             power      = power + fp_u->power*pppm_freqScaling;
04625 
04626         }
04627         //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)
04628 
04629         power      = power + rfu->power*pppm_freqScaling + exeu->power*pppm_freqScaling /*+ bypass.power*/ + scheu->power
04630                            ;
04631 
04632 
04633     }
04634     else
04635     {
04636         set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_alu_accesses, 2, 2, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_alu_accesses);
04637         //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + intTagBypass->power*pppm_t;
04638         //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + int_bypass->power*pppm_t;
04639 
04640         if (coredynp.num_muls >0)
04641         {
04642             set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_mul_accesses, 2, 2, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_mul_accesses);//2 means two source operands needs to be passed for each int instruction.
04643             //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + intTag_mul_Bypass->power*pppm_t + int_mul_bypass->power*pppm_t;
04644             rt_power      = rt_power + mul->rt_power;
04645         }
04646 
04647         if (coredynp.num_fpus>0)
04648         {
04649             set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_fpu_accesses, 3, 3, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_fpu_accesses);
04650             //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + fp_bypass->power*pppm_t;
04651             //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + fpTagBypass->power*pppm_t;
04652             rt_power      = rt_power + fp_u->rt_power;
04653         }
04654         //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)
04655         rt_power      = rt_power + rfu->rt_power*pppm_freqScaling + exeu->rt_power*pppm_freqScaling + /*bypass.rt_power +*/ scheu->rt_power;
04656     }
04657 }
04658 
04659 void EXECU::displayEnergy(uint32_t indent,int plevel,bool is_tdp)
04660 {
04661     if (!exist) return;
04662     string indent_str(indent, ' ');
04663     string indent_str_next(indent+2, ' ');
04664     bool long_channel = XML->sys.longer_channel_device;
04665 
04666 
04667 //  cout << indent_str_next << "Results Broadcast Bus Area = " << bypass->area.get_area() *1e-6 << " mm^2" << endl;
04668     if (is_tdp)
04669     {
04670         cout << indent_str << "Register Files:" << endl;
04671         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << rfu->area.get_area()*1e-6<< " mm^2" << endl;
04672         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << rfu->power.readOp.dynamic*rf_fu_clockRate << " W" << endl;
04673         //cout << "rf_fu Clock rate: "<< rf_fu_clockRate<<endl;
04674         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
04675             << (long_channel? rfu->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:rfu->power.readOp.leakage) <<" W" << endl;
04676         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << rfu->power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
04677         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
04678         cout <<endl;
04679         if (plevel>3){
04680             rfu->displayEnergy(indent+4,is_tdp);
04681         }
04682         cout << indent_str << "Instruction Scheduler:" << endl;
04683         cout << indent_str_next << "Area = " << scheu->area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
04684         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << scheu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04685         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
04686             << (long_channel? scheu->power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:scheu->power.readOp.leakage)  << " W" << endl;
04687         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << scheu->power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
04688         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << scheu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
04689         cout <<endl;
04690         if (plevel>3){
04691             scheu->displayEnergy(indent+4,is_tdp);
04692         }
04693         exeu->displayEnergy(indent,is_tdp);
04694         if (coredynp.num_fpus>0)
04695         {
04696             fp_u->displayEnergy(indent,is_tdp);
04697         }
04698         if (coredynp.num_muls >0)
04699         {
04700             mul->displayEnergy(indent,is_tdp);
04701         }
04702         cout << indent_str << "Results Broadcast Bus:" << endl;
04703         cout << indent_str_next << "Area Overhead = " << bypass.area.get_area()*1e-6  << " mm^2" << endl;
04704         cout << indent_str_next << "Peak Dynamic = " << bypass.power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04705         cout << indent_str_next << "Subthreshold Leakage = "
04706             << (long_channel? bypass.power.readOp.longer_channel_leakage:bypass.power.readOp.leakage ) << " W" << endl;
04707         cout << indent_str_next << "Gate Leakage = " << bypass.power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
04708         cout << indent_str_next << "Runtime Dynamic = " << bypass.rt_power.readOp.dynamic/executionTime << " W" << endl;
04709         cout <<endl;
04710     }
04711     else
04712     {
04713         cout << indent_str_next << "Register Files    Peak Dynamic = " << rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
04714         cout << indent_str_next << "Register Files    Subthreshold Leakage = " << rfu->rt_power.readOp.leakage <<" W" << endl;
04715         cout << indent_str_next << "Register Files    Gate Leakage = " << rfu->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage << " W" << endl;
04716         cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Sheduler   Peak Dynamic = " << scheu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04717         cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Sheduler   Subthreshold Leakage = " << scheu->rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
04718         cout << indent_str_next << "Instruction Sheduler   Gate Leakage = " << scheu->rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
04719         cout << indent_str_next << "Results Broadcast Bus   Peak Dynamic = " << bypass.rt_power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04720         cout << indent_str_next << "Results Broadcast Bus   Subthreshold Leakage = " << bypass.rt_power.readOp.leakage  << " W" << endl;
04721         cout << indent_str_next << "Results Broadcast Bus   Gate Leakage = " << bypass.rt_power.readOp.gate_leakage  << " W" << endl;
04722     }
04723 
04724 }

04730 
04731 //Jingwen
04732 void Core::compute()
04733 {
04734     //power_point_product_masks
04735     double pppm_t[4]    = {1,1,1,1};
04736     double rtp_pipeline_coe;
04737     double num_units = 4.0;
04738     Pipeline_energy=0;
04739 
04740      //Set pipeline duty cycle for this inteval 
04741     coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle=XML->sys.core[ithCore].pipeline_duty_cycle;
04742     rt_power.reset();
04743     ifu->rt_power.reset();
04744     lsu->rt_power.reset();
04745     mmu->rt_power.reset();
04746     exu->rt_power.reset();
04747 
04748 
04749         ifu->computeEnergy(false);
04750         lsu->computeEnergy(false);
04751         mmu->computeEnergy(false);
04752         exu->computeEnergy(false);
04753 
04754 
04755         if (XML->sys.homogeneous_cores==1)
04756         {
04757                 rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * XML->sys.total_cycles * XML->sys.number_of_cores;
04758         }
04759         else
04760         {
04761 
04762             rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * coredynp.total_cycles;
04763             //Jingwen
04764             if (coredynp.total_cycles != XML->sys.total_cycles)
04765             {
04766                 cout << "total cycle not match!" << endl;
04767                 exit(1);
04768             }
04769         }
04770       
04771         set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04772 
04773         if (ifu->exist)
04774         {
04775             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04776             ifu->rt_power = ifu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04777             rt_power     = rt_power + ifu->rt_power ;
04778         }
04779     
04780         if (lsu->exist)
04781         {
04782             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04783             lsu->rt_power = lsu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04784             rt_power     = rt_power  + lsu->rt_power;
04785         }
04786         if (exu->exist)
04787         {
04788             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04789             exu->rt_power = exu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04790             rt_power     = rt_power  + exu->rt_power;
04791         }
04792         if (mmu->exist)
04793         {
04794             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04795             mmu->rt_power = mmu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04796             rt_power     = rt_power +  mmu->rt_power ;
04797         }
04798 
04799         rt_power     = rt_power +  undiffCore->power;
04800     
04801 
04802         if (XML->sys.Private_L2)
04803         {
04804 
04805             l2cache->computeEnergy(false);
04806             rt_power = rt_power  + l2cache->rt_power;
04807         }
04808         
04809         IdleCoreEnergy=XML->sys.num_idle_cores * XML->sys.idle_core_power* executionTime;
04810 
04811         rt_power.readOp.dynamic += IdleCoreEnergy;
04812 
04813 }
04814

04816 
04817 
04818 void Core::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
04819 {
04820     //power_point_product_masks
04821     double pppm_t[4]    = {1,1,1,1};
04822     double rtp_pipeline_coe;
04823     double num_units = 4.0;
04824     Pipeline_energy=0;
04825 
04826     if (XML->sys.homogeneous_cores==1)
04827     {
04828        rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * XML->sys.total_cycles * XML->sys.number_of_cores;
04829     }
04830     else
04831     {
04832        rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * coredynp.total_cycles;
04833     }
04834  
04835 
04836     if (is_tdp)
04837     {
04838         ifu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04839         lsu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04840         mmu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04841         exu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04842 
04843         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
04844         {
04845             num_units = 5.0;
04846             rnu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04847             set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04848             if (rnu->exist)
04849             {
04850                 rnu->power = rnu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04851                 power     = power + rnu->power;
04852             }
04853         }
04854 
04855         if (ifu->exist)
04856         {
04857             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04858             set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.IFU_duty_cycle, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04859 //          cout << "IFU = " << ifu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04860             ifu->power = ifu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04861 //          cout << "IFU = " << ifu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04862 //          cout << "1/4 pipe = " << corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate/num_units  << " W" << endl;
04863             power     = power + ifu->power;
04864 //          cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04865         }
04866         if (lsu->exist)
04867         {
04868             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04869             set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04870             lsu->power = lsu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04871 //          cout << "LSU = " << lsu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04872             power     = power + lsu->power;
04873 //          cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04874         }
04875         if (exu->exist)
04876         {
04877             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04878             set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04879             //cout<<"ExPowerScalingFactor:"<<coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle<<endl;
04880             exu->power = exu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04881 //          cout << "EXE = " << exu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04882             power     = power + exu->power;
04883 //          cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04884         }
04885         if (mmu->exist)
04886         {
04887             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04888             set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*(0.5+0.5*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle), coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04889             mmu->power = mmu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04890 //          cout << "MMU = " << mmu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04891             power     = power +  mmu->power;
04892 //          cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04893         }
04894 
04895         power     = power +  undiffCore->power;
04896 
04897         if (XML->sys.Private_L2)
04898         {
04899 
04900             l2cache->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04901             set_pppm(pppm_t,l2cache->cachep.clockRate/clockRate, 1,1,1);
04902             //l2cache->power = l2cache->power*pppm_t;
04903             power = power  + l2cache->power*pppm_t;
04904         }
04905 
04906     }
04907     else
04908     {
04909     rt_power.reset();
04910 
04911 
04912 
04913 
04914         ifu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04915         lsu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04916         mmu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04917         exu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04918         if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
04919         {
04920             num_units = 5.0;
04921             rnu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04922             set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04923             if (rnu->exist)
04924             {
04925             rnu->rt_power = rnu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04926 
04927             rt_power      = rt_power + rnu->rt_power;
04928             }
04929         }
04930         else
04931         {
04932 
04933             set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
04934         }
04935 
04936         if (ifu->exist)
04937         {
04938             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04939             ifu->rt_power = ifu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04940             rt_power     = rt_power + ifu->rt_power ;
04941         }
04942         if (lsu->exist)
04943         {
04944             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04945             lsu->rt_power = lsu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04946             rt_power     = rt_power  + lsu->rt_power;
04947         }
04948         if (exu->exist)
04949         {
04950             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04951             exu->rt_power = exu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04952             rt_power     = rt_power  + exu->rt_power;
04953         }
04954         if (mmu->exist)
04955         {
04956             Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
04957             mmu->rt_power = mmu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
04958             rt_power     = rt_power +  mmu->rt_power ;
04959         }
04960 
04961         rt_power     = rt_power +  undiffCore->power;
04962 //      cout << "EXE = " << exu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate  << " W" << endl;
04963         if (XML->sys.Private_L2)
04964         {
04965             l2cache->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
04966             //set_pppm(pppm_t,1/l2cache->cachep.executionTime, 1,1,1);
04967             //l2cache->rt_power = l2cache->rt_power*pppm_t;
04968             rt_power = rt_power  + l2cache->rt_power;
04969         }
04970 
04971     }
04972 
04973 }
